'''Allen McCarthy''' ([[July 11]], [[1957]] - [[August 11]], [[1995]]) was a [[Canada|Canadian]] musician born in [[Montreal, Quebec]] who became part of the group [[Men Without Hats]].
"Men Without Hats" disbanded in 1992 and three years later McCarthy died of an [[AIDS]]-related death at the age of 38. He is buried in the [[Mount Royal Cemetery]] in Montreal.
